Isle of Everywhere is a music track that is unlocked on the east coast of Lunar Isle.

Versions[edit | edit source]

Version Release Music Track
1 10 April 2006
2 6 March 2007

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Until 17 March 2021, it could also be unlocked by scrying through a Lunar Isle portal in a player-owned house. This allowed players who have not started the Lunar Diplomacy quest, such as one-defence pures, to unlock the track.
